Let’s refine the architecture deeply.

1. EC2 → S3 Access Model

You already understood this correctly.

EC2
 ↓
IAM Role attached to EC2
 ↓
Temporary credentials generated by AWS STS
 ↓
SDK/API calls signed automatically
